Symbol.Script_3D:
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_OFF THEN 999
Unid=1
!!! *** Length
!!! >>> Length
HOTSPOT 0, 0, ZZYZX, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, 0, ZZYZX, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, 0, ZZYZX, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, B, ZZYZX, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -1, B, ZZYZX, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B, ZZYZX, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
!!! >>> Width
HOTSPOT A, 0, ZZYZX, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, -1, ZZYZX, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B, ZZYZX, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0, 0, ZZYZX, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -1, ZZYZX, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B, ZZYZX, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
!!! >>> Height HOTSPOT 0,B/2,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B/2,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,B/2,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,B/2,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B/2,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,B/2,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1
!!! >>> Web Thickness ADDY B/2 HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID,stee_th2,1+128, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-stee_th2,0,unID,stee_th2,2, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,1,0,unID,stee_th2,3, stee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A,0,0,unID,stee_th2,1+128, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,stee_th2,0,unID,stee_th2,2, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A,-1,0,unID,stee_th2,3, stee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,stee_th2,1+128, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-stee_th2,0,unID,stee_th2,2, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,1,0,unID,stee_th2,3, stee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,stee_th2,1+128, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,stee_th2,0,unID,stee_th2,2, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,-1,0,unID,stee_th2,3, stee_th : unID=unID+1 DEL 1
if not(gs_shadow) then shadow off
ADDy B/2 PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL gs_stee_mat
FOR w=1 TO nn*2 PUT GET (2), MAX (-1, 15*GET (1)) NEXT w PUT 0, 0, 777
ROTz 90 ROTx 90 PRISM_ NSP/3, a, GET (NSP) IF dtee_top_th>0 THEN PRISM_ 4, a, -b/2, zzyzx+0.001, 8, -b/2, zzyzx+dtee_top_th, 13, b/2, zzyzx+dtee_top_th, 8, b/2, zzyzx+0.001, 13 ENDIF DEL 2 DEL 1
999: FOR w=1 TO NSP qq= GET (1) NEXT w
END
Symbol.Script_2D:
PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type
Unid=1
! --- Length
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, B, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
! --- Width
HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, -1, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, B, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -1, unID, B, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID, B, 2 : unID=unID+1
! --- Length/Axis
HOTSPOT2 0, B/2, unID, A, 1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, B/2, unID, A, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B/2, unID, A, 2 : unID=unID+1
! --- Center
HOTSPOT2 A/2, B/2, unID : unID=unID+1
Unid=100
if only_axis=0 then ! --- Web Thickness if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED then ADD2 0,B/2 HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,stee_th2,1+128, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-stee_th2,unID,stee_th2,2, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,1,unID,stee_th2,3, stee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 A,0,unID,stee_th2,1+128, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,stee_th2,unID,stee_th2,2, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A,-1,unID,stee_th2,3, stee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,stee_th2,1+128, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-stee_th2,unID,stee_th2,2, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,1,unID,stee_th2,3, stee_th : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID,stee_th2,1+128, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,stee_th2,unID,stee_th2,2, stee_th : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,-1,unID,stee_th2,3, stee_th : unID=unID+1 DEL 1 endif endif
ADD2 0,B/2
if only_axis=0 then
POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, -b/2, 1, 0, b/2, 1, a, b/2, 1, a, -b/2, 1, 0, -b/2, -1
if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED then LINE_TYPE DetailLineType
LINE2 0, th/2, a, th/2 LINE2 0, -th/2, a, -th/2 endif
endif
Unid=200 if showsect AND only_axis=0 then LINE_TYPE 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, pos_2Dx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -1', unID, pos_2Dx, 3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 pos_2Dx, 0, unID, pos_2Dx, 2 : unID=unID+1 ADD2 pos_2Dx, 0 ROT2 90 FILL cross_fill POLY2_ NSP/3, 7, GET (NSP) DEL 2 endif
if axis then PEN axis_pen LINE_TYPE axis_line_type
LINE2 0, 0, a, 0 endif
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! iObjectCode PRE_BEAM_SINGLE_T = 11
rrr = request("Working_length_unit", "", w_units_form) bMetricDimension = strstr(w_units_form, "m") ! m, cm, mm
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iDet2D DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 2
PUT zzyzx, b, stee_th, stee_h2, stee_h4
IF NSP>=5 THEN zz = GET (1) w1 = GET (1) th = GET (1) h2 = GET (1) h4 = GET (1) zzyzx = zz PARAMETERS zzyzx = zz b = w1 PARAMETERS b = w1 h3 = ((b-th)/2-h2)/14 h1 = zzyzx-h4-h3-h2 PUT 5 PUT -th/2, 0, 1, -th/2, h1, 1, -th/2-h2, h1+h2, 1, -b/2+0.001, zz-h4, 1, -b/2+0.001, zz, 1 ENDIF
! *** Contour mirroring *** DIM xy[][3]
IF NSP>0 THEN nn = round_int(get(1)) FOR w =1 TO nn xx = GET (1) yy = GET (1) msk = GET (1) PUT xx, yy, msk xy[w][1] = -xx xy[w][2] = yy xy[w][3] = msk NEXT w
FOR w = nn TO 1 STEP -1 PUT xy[w][1], xy[w][2], xy[w][3] NEXT w ENDIF ! *** *** ***

"geometryPage":

outfieldHeight = 15 infieldHeight = 19
dy = 24 yEnd = 266 pageStartY = 0 yCurrent = pageStartY + 1
ui_style 0, 0

ui_separator 0, yCurrent, xEnd, yCurrent
uiPictX = 50 uiPictY = yCurrent + 64 uiPictWdt = 243 uiPictHgt = 102 uiPictMargin = 5 uiPictInfWdt = 90
uiPicLeftStart = uiPictX - uiPictInfWdt - uiPictMargin uiPicLeftEND = uiPicLeftStart - uiPictMargin
uiPicTop = uiPictY - uiPictMargin - infieldHeight + 3
uiPicBelow = uiPictY + uiPictHgt + uiPictMargin
uiPicRightStart = uiPictX + uiPictWdt + uiPictMargin

if bTopping then ui_infield "dtee_top_th", uiPictX+240, uiPicTop, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина Покрытия` endif
ui_infield "stee_th", uiPictX+138, uiPicBelow, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Толщина Стенки Внизу`
ui_infield "stee_h4", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+10, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Высота Полки Вверху` ui_infield "stee_h2", uiPicRightStart, uiPictY+30, uiPictInfWdt, infieldHeight UI_TOOLTIP `Скос Вверху`
return

Symbol.Script_VL:
hideparameter all ”A”, ”B”, ”Zzyzx”
call "FM_types" parameters all
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "bTopping" then if not(bTopping) then parameters dtee_top_th = 0 lock "dtee_top_th" else parameters dtee_top_th = 0.030 endif endif
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values{2} "iDet2D" DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE, `Простой`
VALUES "a" RANGE (0.3, ) VALUES "b" RANGE [stee_th+0.1, ) VALUES "stee_th" RANGE [0.05, b/2] VALUES "stee_h4" RANGE [0.02, ZZYZX-0.1) VALUES "stee_h2" RANGE [0.02, b/6] VALUES "zzyzx" RANGE [MAX (0.15, stee_h4+stee_h2+(b/2-stee_th/2-stee_h2)/14), ) VALUES "stee_th2" RANGE [0.05/2, b/4]
if LibraryLangCode = "USA" then VALUES "stee_sectype" "10STxx", "Custom"
if stee_sectype="10STxx" then VALUES "stee_type" "10ST12", "10ST16", "10ST20", "10ST24", "10ST28", "10ST32", "10ST36", "10ST40", "10ST44", "10ST48" else lock "stee_type" endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stee_type" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stee_sectype" then if stee_sectype="10STxx" then if stee_type="10ST12" then zzyzx = 12" if stee_type="10ST16" then zzyzx = 16" if stee_type="10ST20" then zzyzx = 20" if stee_type="10ST24" then zzyzx = 24" if stee_type="10ST28" then zzyzx = 28" if stee_type="10ST32" then zzyzx = 32" if stee_type="10ST36" then zzyzx = 36" if stee_type="10ST40" then zzyzx = 40" if stee_type="10ST44" then zzyzx = 44" if stee_type="10ST48" then zzyzx = 48" b = 10' stee_th = 8" stee_h2 = 3" stee_h4 = 1.5" parameters zzyzx = zzyzx, b = b, stee_th = stee_th, stee_h2 = stee_h2, stee_h4 = stee_h4 endif endif
! set back to custom if main parameters are changed if stee_sectype <> "Custom" then if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ZZYZX" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stee_th" or \ GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stee_h2" or GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stee_h4" then stee_sectype = "Custom" parameters stee_sectype = stee_sectype endif endif else hideparameter "stee_sectype", "stee_type" endif
VALUES "pos_2Dx" RANGE (zzyzx, a)
VALUES "dtee_top_th" RANGE [0,)
if not(axis) then parameters only_axis=0 lock "only_axis", "axis_line_type", "axis_pen" endif if not(showsect) then lock "cross_fill" endif if axis and only_axis then lock "gs_fill_type", "gs_fill_pen", "gs_back_pen", "showsect", "cross_fill", "iDet2D", "DetailLineType", "gs_cont_pen" endif
if iDet2D = DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE then lock "DetailLineType" endif
FOR w=1 TO NSP/3 PUT GET (2) qq= GET (1) NEXT w IF NSP>0 THEN PUT 1 PUT GET (NSP-1) ENDIF
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME ="stee_th" THEN PARAMETERS stee_th2=stee_th/2 IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME ="stee_th2" THEN PARAMETERS stee_th=stee_th2*2
IF gs_cont_pen = 0 then parameters gs_cont_pen = 10 IF gs_fill_pen = 0 then parameters gs_fill_pen = 19
es_length=a es_surface = b*(stee_h4+zzyzx-stee_h4-stee_h2-((b-stee_th)/2-stee_h2)/14)/2! + stee_h2^2 + (stee_h2+zzyzx-stee_h4-((b-stee_th)/2-stee_h2)/14)*stee_th es_volume = es_surface*es_length PARAMETERS es_length=es_length, es_surface = es_surface, es_volume = es_volume
CALL "Precast_quantity_calc" parameters A = A, bMetricDimension = bMetricDimension, es_density = es_density, es_density_us = es_density_us, es_volume = es_volume, es_surface = es_surface
